## 🔥 Fronti caldi
```dataview
table without id file.link as Nome, pressione as Pressione, prossima_mossa as "Prossima mossa"
from ""
where categoria = "{{ page.category }}" and pressione >= 5 and stato != "archiviata"
sort pressione desc
limit 8
```

